gi toilet. \u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKalau kita perasan kat petrol station cthnya Petronas,  ada toilet yg kt dlm kedai Mesra tu sendiri, ada yg luar sikit sebelah  dgn kedai Mesra dan ada jugak toilet yang bahagian belakanggg, jauh  sikit dr kedai Mesra tu. Yup, she went to that toilet, yg kat belakang  tu, ALONE AT NIGHT, while the boyfriend was waiting in the car. \u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003ESelepas  30 minit menunggu, this girl tak muncul, dia terus pergi ke toilet  belakang tu untuk cari. Dia jumpa girlfriend dia pengsan dan dalam  keadaan yang agak aib (suspected dirogol). Sadly, it is true. Somebody  grabbed her when she was entering the toilet, tutup mulut dia, kunci  toilet and violently, she was being raped. Couldn't really tell who, but  through what she could see, the person is black (and she suspected a  negro). \u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKesian sangat2 kat mangsa ni sebab dia akan berkahwin tak lama  lagi dan dia berada dalam keadaan yang sangat trauma dan tertekan  sekarang. Of course, who wouldn't right! Nauzubillah kalau itu terjadi  kt kita\/keluarga kita.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E So, tolonglahh jgn pergi toilet sorang2  especially yg jauh kt hujung dunia nun regardless mlm or siang. Please  be extra careful, get somebody (kawan, adik, tunang, suami, anak,  anyone) untuk teman walaupun rasa tak macho sebab kena tunggu depan  toilet, but safety firstt!! It could happen to anyone, bertudung ke free  hair ke, anyone could be vulnerable (this girl is wearing hijab, so  lets not assume that rape is inclined to happen to those wearing  revealing clothes ONLY). Just be extra cautious, peeps\u003C\/span\u003E"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/gempaqgiler.blogspot.com\/feeds\/4723984248536875176\/comments\/default","title":"Catat Ulasan"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/gempaqgiler.blogspot.com\/2014\/05\/kisah-benar-wanita-dirogol-negro-ketika.html#comment-form","tit